The paper discusses the use of distributed algorithms among mobile robots, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the use of movement-signals and communication protocols, which are related to multi-agent systems (cs.MA) and distributed systems (cs.DS). The paper also mentions the use of stigmergic robots, which is a type of swarm robotics (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses the use of recognition mechanisms and implicit acknowledgments, which are related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
